   610‚Üí  /**
   611‚Üí   * Calculate the pad width from the maximum term length.
   612‚Üí   *
   613‚Üí   * @param {Command} cmd
   614‚Üí   * @param {Help} helper
   615‚Üí   * @returns {number}
